{"tid":202268,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"學「砌機」一流！新 Game 將砌機變打機 [有片]","createTime":"2017-04-15T11:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T11:09:47.000Z","uid":1886,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dcf61294efe937c0a2e8941888dd23a22f441531","tid":202268,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:22:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>學「砌機」一流！新 Game 將砌機變打機 [有片]<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.price.com.hk/news.php?sec_id=14&amp;id=7620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fnews.php%3Fsec_id%3D14%26id%3D7620&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=e9817260\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.price.com.hk/news.php?sec_id=14&amp;id=7620</a></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.price.com.hk/space/news/images/20170316/1725d7a0c3e554e033c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fspace%2Fnews%2Fimages%2F20170316%2F1725d7a0c3e554e033c6.jpg&h=070654ce&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n大部分人都知道自己「砌機」比起從各大電腦牌子買一部原廠機划算得多。不過砌機對很多人來說都是高級技術，覺得要很大量心機和時間去鑽研才學得懂。如果你也有興趣學砌機，甚至本身就喜歡砌機，現在有個很好的途徑來試試：遊戲。<br />\n<br />\nPC Building Simulator 顧名思義就是「砌機模擬器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，真實地讓你嘗試整個砌機過程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。首先你會有一個限定的預算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，然後就要在預算範圍內選購各個零件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。下一步就要將零件逐一砌入機殼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，再上螺絲和接合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。如果未能成功開機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，就要看看究竟是哪裡出問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">示範片：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kxi0yEgbuc8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dkxi0yEgbuc8&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=e094f578\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kxi0yEgbuc8</a></div><br />\n<br />\n開發者表示這個遊戲是想讓人們用一個有趣的方式親自試試砌機，又可以不用花一分一毫就能練習和試驗。現時遊戲還在 pre-alpha 測試階段，所以內容比較簡單，畫面不算太吸引。之後會陸續豐富內容，包括加入「砌機佬」模式，挑戰經營砌機生意來賺錢。有興趣可以去官網下載。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://mcintyre.itch.io/pc-building-simulator\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmcintyre.itch.io%2Fpc-building-simulator&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=2f5dcf3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://mcintyre.itch.io/pc-building-simulator</a></div>"},{"pid":"f15bc889ee362953db556ccbad5939bb54970d6a","tid":202268,"uid":17352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:23:18.000Z","msg":"幾得意喎<br />\n出左可以買黎玩下"},{"pid":"9f50a16746e1b65b306c7c6fc4c2364f63fd7db0","tid":202268,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T11:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e0d2d052ab3b2f68f602b615348ba3fef21c98","tid":202268,"uid":73384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T05:04:56.000Z","msg":"留名支持"},{"pid":"8532b4edd285f4e5efdc618357a6c0d491b05c8f","tid":202268,"uid":96246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:48:17.000Z","msg":"之前都想搵呢類software<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac5335a0c8ba5ee71d32cb47ffa497ebb3bdc92","tid":202268,"uid":96246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前都想搵呢類software<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來真係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bee1223ebed3b0e20116c8a172171b5a2a89b1","tid":202268,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d94271634cb59c77705b76ffe9ba45bd3201861","tid":202268,"uid":61735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:52:28.000Z","msg":"Complete version<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bc8cd6135bb92acd6d099a44cc618d50904c1e","tid":202268,"uid":15199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:52:36.000Z","msg":"最撚煩係走線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49528b7be67f91cea0da713525daec1393ed3ad7","tid":202268,"uid":72929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T19:02:30.000Z","msg":"幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d64651f88c98f72a40b35865d4e205ae8ec7647","tid":202268,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:29:41.000Z","msg":"係咪有曬咁多間廠嘅hardware<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346284554ed21158b197ef64766d73910577016f","tid":202268,"uid":40315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc37881c3d27351ff0f89fbf9853b8e9f191447","tid":202268,"uid":86775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2767a57c66006cc3e8efae77b80cb83d0e5f4a","tid":202268,"uid":56138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T16:18:31.000Z","msg":"出咗鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日買嚟玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9466252e6521abab00dc4d8da4ceb052f3cbca1f","tid":202268,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:07:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://g1infos.blogspot.hk/2018/03/pc-building-simulatordesktop-steam.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg1infos.blogspot.hk%2F2018%2F03%2Fpc-building-simulatordesktop-steam.html&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=bbdbac90\" target=\"_blank\">https://g1infos.blogspot.hk/2018/03/pc-building-simulatordesktop-steam.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">已推出<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-nuBCuXZCAp0/WsBt5EMAl3I/AAAAAAAAAIY/oLZkiMVRwGQ2ORVaQrPgy35i1LL1eK7cQCLcBGAs/s640/pc-building-simulator.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-nuBCuXZCAp0%2FWsBt5EMAl3I%2FAAAAAAAAAIY%2FoLZkiMVRwGQ2ORVaQrPgy35i1LL1eK7cQCLcBGAs%2Fs640%2Fpc-building-simulator.png&h=3cd8a79c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSteam 最近推出了一款模擬遊戲《PC Building Simulator》，玩法就是玩家利用不同的硬件組裝一部desktop電腦，而電腦裡CPU，顯示卡，主機版motherboard甚至是機箱都全由玩家自已選擇。<br />\n<br />\n由於《PC Building Simulator》得到了眾多電腦硬件商協助，遊戲裡的PC硬件和現實是完全一樣的，即是你是可以根據遊戲中的電腦硬件Config在現實裡組裝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-0_y7DTSQlC0/WsBuDYFCKeI/AAAAAAAAAIg/RBy_oEQMCXgEDa6DxjMjjSJ6QxInr9PXACEwYBhgL/s400/pc-building-simulator3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-0_y7DTSQlC0%2FWsBuDYFCKeI%2FAAAAAAAAAIg%2FRBy_oEQMCXgEDa6DxjMjjSJ6QxInr9PXACEwYBhgL%2Fs400%2Fpc-building-simulator3.png&h=c35dd51d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Ci32CJmvxh4/WsBuCeb5nfI/AAAAAAAAAIc/rc81bfC7hRwWIP0vI8bo9zewxJ8Ynuy1QCEwYBhgL/s400/pc-building-simulator2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Ci32CJmvxh4%2FWsBuCeb5nfI%2FAAAAAAAAAIc%2Frc81bfC7hRwWIP0vI8bo9zewxJ8Ynuy1QCEwYBhgL%2Fs400%2Fpc-building-simulator2.png&h=0c1e0ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲設有劇情模式玩家扮演主角剛剛創立了一間砌機公司，需要根據客人要求完成指定任務。任務內容亦相當有趣，除了普通組裝一部新電腦外，亦會有為客人安裝防毒程式及為客人升級指定部份硬件等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uDbvssbEU5Q/WsBuTO5BcTI/AAAAAAAAAIk/3anoAiTli_wete05tWnBqiZWzPRCKsMngCLcBGAs/s400/pc-building-simulator-4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-uDbvssbEU5Q%2FWsBuTO5BcTI%2FAAAAAAAAAIk%2F3anoAiTli_wete05tWnBqiZWzPRCKsMngCLcBGAs%2Fs400%2Fpc-building-simulator-4.png&h=c9e1c890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-yCWqqiWpaKQ/WsBuTZNh5PI/AAAAAAAAAIo/FyXdSG-bepEpvngSMHi9TLr2hbMxZDWMgCLcBGAs/s400/pc-building-simulator-5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-yCWqqiWpaKQ%2FWsBuTZNh5PI%2FAAAAAAAAAIo%2FFyXdSG-bepEpvngSMHi9TLr2hbMxZDWMgCLcBGAs%2Fs400%2Fpc-building-simulator-5.png&h=5e9f1b02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0475be8ba77ad76824df9bf6a6695ae64046fd09","tid":202268,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:08:31.000Z","msg":"當中一個任務就是客人要求加 RAM，在遊戲中玩家需要先拆開電腦，然後玩家先清理主機內部的積塵，再從倉庫取出需要的RAM、最後取出客人電腦內的 RAM，把新的RAM插進電腦中。在遊戲中玩家選擇插一條 8GB RAM或4GB RAM x2都沒有問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-D0JwtUc_Yws/WsBuTVfyqAI/AAAAAAAAAIs/_AMFfC2OitAdLY8qXTGISlLJ4VrG_6IZACLcBGAs/s400/pc-building-simulator-6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-D0JwtUc_Yws%2FWsBuTVfyqAI%2FAAAAAAAAAIs%2F_AMFfC2OitAdLY8qXTGISlLJ4VrG_6IZACLcBGAs%2Fs400%2Fpc-building-simulator-6.png&h=22bcf586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-n2L1fC44ZiQ/WsBuoeY8M1I/AAAAAAAAAI8/m46bjmV4IbwJ5XhdwxirVwe3kMtk_aEuACLcBGAs/s400/pc-building-simulator-7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-n2L1fC44ZiQ%2FWsBuoeY8M1I%2FAAAAAAAAAI8%2Fm46bjmV4IbwJ5XhdwxirVwe3kMtk_aEuACLcBGAs%2Fs400%2Fpc-building-simulator-7.png&h=158c1780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-tJKA7P66bA0/WsBunRJ24FI/AAAAAAAAAI4/mk-CplONyYAudFeS7zCdaU2Zqzz3SIJUQCLcBGAs/s400/pc-building-simulator-8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-tJKA7P66bA0%2FWsBunRJ24FI%2FAAAAAAAAAI4%2Fmk-CplONyYAudFeS7zCdaU2Zqzz3SIJUQCLcBGAs%2Fs400%2Fpc-building-simulator-8.png&h=24264da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而在修理過程取得的二手零件，更可以留給下一個客人使用，或在自己的電腦上使用。遊戲自由度相當高，玩家甚至可以做「無良奸商」，利用各種方法賺更多的錢，確保公司不會破產而「Game Over」！"},{"pid":"afeb8bf4740eb09208c4bc88eb8a70db73825a65","tid":202268,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:08:55.000Z","msg":"遊戲如現實一樣設有 Benchmark，玩家需要成功運行「3DMark」，電腦沒有問題才算完成任務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-VCN5rFhlLt8/WsBu4x7reeI/AAAAAAAAAJQ/urqk5OSOq9AQgynkEzjaRJSxzKjjc86YgCLcBGAs/s400/pc-building-simulator-9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-VCN5rFhlLt8%2FWsBu4x7reeI%2FAAAAAAAAAJQ%2Furqk5OSOq9AQgynkEzjaRJSxzKjjc86YgCLcBGAs%2Fs400%2Fpc-building-simulator-9.png&h=128a78e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Xh72wi8kSQ8/WsBu4mqjbZI/AAAAAAAAAJM/NfU25ODzSsw-Ebk_Wf3vzBO5HIDkmpCnwCLcBGAs/s400/pc-building-simulator%253D10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Xh72wi8kSQ8%2FWsBu4mqjbZI%2FAAAAAAAAAJM%2FNfU25ODzSsw-Ebk_Wf3vzBO5HIDkmpCnwCLcBGAs%2Fs400%2Fpc-building-simulator%25253D10.png&h=c4196a72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"deaaf3ffc60ee609430090dc58ef38f899e74dd5","tid":202268,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:09:37.000Z","msg":"遊戲亦設有 自由組裝模式，玩家可以自由組裝一部理想的desktop 電腦。玩家在商店裡面可購買顯示卡、CPU、主機板、記憶體、HDD / SSD、火牛、機箱、散熱器、工具等等。 MSI GeForce GTX 系列都能夠在遊戲中找到。 Arctic, Cooler Master, GIGABYTE, MSI, Corsair，還有 AMD 的 Ryzen 以及 Radeon 都能在遊戲中一一找到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3ylw6ktO2nE/WsBvDcqFdTI/AAAAAAAAAJc/r4Yz50Z3RMkKrWUqIhbWVXdmRwSR5c2QQCLcBGAs/s400/pc-building-simulator-11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-3ylw6ktO2nE%2FWsBvDcqFdTI%2FAAAAAAAAAJc%2Fr4Yz50Z3RMkKrWUqIhbWVXdmRwSR5c2QQCLcBGAs%2Fs400%2Fpc-building-simulator-11.png&h=a0043994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-NOcfnbp5BzY/WsBvDYrPTKI/AAAAAAAAAJY/HwBM7zSW090-Y25-A_JovZSdlCDyofBewCLcBGAs/s400/pc-building-simulator-12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-NOcfnbp5BzY%2FWsBvDYrPTKI%2FAAAAAAAAAJY%2FHwBM7zSW090-Y25-A_JovZSdlCDyofBewCLcBGAs%2Fs400%2Fpc-building-simulator-12.png&h=fa20a964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-66CNHonwcKY/WsBvDICFdPI/AAAAAAAAAJU/C4RshnL9JY4eAXtl9FQBim9rQf7CcsQKQCLcBGAs/s400/pc-building-simulator-13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-66CNHonwcKY%2FWsBvDICFdPI%2FAAAAAAAAAJU%2FC4RshnL9JY4eAXtl9FQBim9rQf7CcsQKQCLcBGAs%2Fs400%2Fpc-building-simulator-13.png&h=31e741b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩家選購好硬件後，CPU Socket 、電源等都要符合需求。然後再組裝到主機裡。遊戲更提供電腦機箱與主機板的 LED 燈光顏色選擇。如果大家對砌機不熟悉，遊戲設有「How to Build a PC」模式，完整砌機教學。"},{"pid":"6be7125eeff33d119b411032fa333c43935cab4d","tid":202268,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:09:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/621060/PC_Building_Simulator/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F621060%2FPC_Building_Simulator%2F&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=f8361213\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/621060/PC_Building_Simulator/</a>"}]}